data.description: 3-2-Oversized 2+Sunroom. NO CARPET! This recently renovated beauty features an inviting living area with a wood burning fireplace and beamed, vaulted ceilings. Enjoy a morning coffee in the vented sunroom, and fill the oversized garage with toys. The property boasts mature trees, a large backyard, and a tall back fence. Attic has been insulated with open cell spray foam (protects pipes in freezing temps). PVC sewage line. No concessions at current price.
